node.text:
How incredible is Siwa Oasis in Egypt? 🇪🇬 💙 "Siwa lakes are considered to have healing properties for sinus, skin, and eye conditions, which have allowed the oasis to be promoted as a medical and recreational destination. The water here has a salt concentration of more than 95%."

Tag someone who should see this! 🤯

📽 @flyyestguy
📍 Siwa Oasis, Egypt
🎶 Egyptian Pools - Jinsang

node.text:
The new residential Mega Yacht ‘Somnio’ will be the largest yacht in the world when it launches in 2024. 🔥

This 728 feet mansion will have 39 apartments across 6 floors, with apartment prices starting from $11,000,000 with an invite only to purchase. The cost of the project is to be around $600,000,000 and it will be built in Norway. 🛥

📷 @winchdesign_wd
📍Monte-Carlo, Monaco

node.text:
Dolomites in Italy 🇮🇹 A group of craggy mountains nestled in the Italian Alps, the Dolomites is a picturesque scenery that never fails to impress. ⛰

The Italian Dolomites always highly distinctive mountain landscapes that are of exceptional natural beauty. It's home to all kinds of mountain activities, and delicious cuisine making for a truly unforgettable holiday.

Have you been to the Dolomites or would you love to? 😍

💃 @rebe.twosoles
📽 @alex.twosoles
📍 Dolomites, Italy
🎶 Adam Fediy - Wildest Dreams (Music Inspired by "Bridgerton")

node.text:
Diving headfirst into the weekend like… ☁️ Wingsuit flying (or wingsuiting) is the sport of flying through the air using a wingsuit which adds surface area to the human body to enable a significant increase in lift. 

This wingsuit flight was shoot in Montserrat Natural Park, a multi-peaked mountain range near Barcelona, in Catalonia, Spain.

"Montserrat" literally means "serrated (like the common handsaw) mountain" in Catalan. It describes its peculiar aspect with a multitude of rock formations that are visible from a great distance. The mountain is composed of strikingly pink conglomerate, a form of sedimentary rock.

📽 @daniroman_ @fredfugen @vincent.cotte @bras.noir
📍Montserrant, Spain
